     I*
     I* Error processing source
     I*
     I*-------------------------------------------------------------------
     I* Message field definitions:
     I*
     I#MSDTA      DS
     I                                        1 132 #MSDFA
     I#MSDFB      DS
     I                                        1 132 #MSTX1
     I#MSTX2      DS
     I                                        1 256 #MSTXA
