     C/EJECT
     C********************************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           #MSGID
     C                     PARM           #MSDTA
     C*
     C* Add subroutine name to stack:
     C*
     C                     Z-ADD1         Q       30
     C                     MOVEL'@Main@'  @STK,Q
     C*
     C* Move the copyright text:
     C*
     C                     MOVEACPY@      ACT@   80
     C*
     C* Get the text of the required message:
     C*
     C                     CALL 'CGC1000'              9090
     C                     PARM           #MSGID  7
     C                     PARM 'CGUSRMSG'#MSGF  10
     C                     PARM           #MSDTA
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   #MSTX1
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   #MSTX2
     C*
     C                     MOVEL#MSTX1    #STATE
     C*
     C* Display the message:
     C                     WRITE#WINDOW
     C*
     C* To keep the compiler happy:
     C*
     C  N25 25             READ #WINDOW                  25
     C*
     C* Unwind subroutine stack:
     C*
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   @STK,Q
     C                     SUB  1         Q
     C*
     C                     RETRN
